Purpose.quote: "For I know the plans I have for you," declares the Lord, "plans to prosper you and not to harm you, plans to give you hope and a future." (Jeremiah 29:11)

Divine Will.quote: "Not my will, but yours be done." (Luke 22:42)

Providence.quote: "In their hearts humans plan their course, but the Lord establishes their steps." (Proverbs 16:9)

Predestination.quote: "Those whom He foreknew, He also predestined to be conformed to the image of His Son." (Romans 8:29)

Divine Order.quote: "From Him and through Him and to Him are all things." (Romans 11:36)

Cosmic Design.quote: "He has made everything beautiful in its time." (Ecclesiastes 3:11)

Divine Guidance.quote: "Your word is a lamp for my feet, a light on my path." (Psalm 119:105)

Divine Timing.quote: "To everything there is a season, and a time to every purpose under heaven." (Ecclesiastes 3:1)

Divine Intention.quote: "According to the eternal purpose which He accomplished in Christ Jesus our Lord." (Ephesians 3:11)

Divine Strategy.quote: "The Lord works out everything to its proper end." (Proverbs 16:4)

Divine Mission.quote: "Go therefore and make disciples of all nations." (Matthew 28:19)

Divine Destiny.quote: "Before I formed you in the womb I knew you." (Jeremiah 1:5)

Divine Blueprint.quote: "In the beginning was the Word, and the Word was with God, and the Word was God." (John 1:1)

Divine Purpose.quote: "For everything created by God is good, and nothing is to be rejected." (1 Timothy 4:4)

Divine Direction.quote: "Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding." (Proverbs 3:5)

Divine Orchestration.quote: "And we know that in all things God works for the good of those who love him." (Romans 8:28)

Divine Wisdom.quote: "O the depth of the riches both of the wisdom and knowledge of God!" (Romans 11:33)

Divine Arrangement.quote: "The lot is cast into the lap, but its every decision is from the Lord." (Proverbs 16:33)

Divine Schedule.quote: "But when the set time had fully come, God sent his Son." (Galatians 4:4)

Divine Providence.quote: "Your eyes saw my unformed body; all the days ordained for me were written in your book before one of them came to be." (Psalm 139:16)

Divine Decree.quote: "I make known the end from the beginning, from ancient times, what is still to come." (Isaiah 46:10)

Divine Design.quote: "For we are God's handiwork, created in Christ Jesus to do good works, which God prepared in advance for us to do." (Ephesians 2:10)

Divine Program.quote: "There are different kinds of gifts, but the same Spirit distributes them." (1 Corinthians 12:4)

Divine Goals.quote: "That in the dispensation of the fullness of times He might gather together in one all things in Christ." (Ephesians 1:10)

Divine Method.quote: "As the heavens are higher than the earth, so are my ways higher than your ways and my thoughts than your thoughts." (Isaiah 55:9)

Divine Path.quote: "I am the way, the truth, and the life." (John 14:6)

Divine Process.quote: "Being confident of this, that he who began a good work in you will carry it on to completion." (Philippians 1:6)

Divine Implementation.quote: "Not by might, nor by power, but by my Spirit." (Zechariah 4:6)

Divine Outcome.quote: "For the earth will be filled with the knowledge of the glory of the Lord as the waters cover the sea." (Habakkuk 2:14)
